social_posts.post_text:
@nbcsnl @brandicarlile 
I’m a lifelong fan of SNL. I watch every week with very few exceptions. It’s not an exaggeration.  I can’t believe we’ve done this twice now. It was a good thing I was taking pictures backstage because I was nervously eating lifesavers every time I didn’t have my camera in hand. #whoateallthecandy
Happy ten year anniversary to my love. We spend so much time together it’s weird, and I’m still obsessed with you. I didn’t know life could be this good @timhanseroth
In no particular order, some of my favorites from @justwannaweekend

This past weekend at @gorgeamphitheatre was filled with so many big moments…but here is a small one. Walking with my husband off stage. Very proud to be a part of this team of humans, who bring other humans together. ❤️ 
Thank you @ludaronkycaptures for the 📸

Happy Birthday to the love of my life.
@timhanseroth
One of my favorites of @joyoladokun  at @redrocksco. More of my favorites from August and September (so far) in my stories.
December light in the upper left.

Yes, social media says I should post a recap from 2023. I will, because I am proud of the images I took in 2023. However I ALSO took this picture of my sisters and me, taking a break from our LOTR marathon, to have a walk.  Because documenting small delights/brilliant things from my life is something I want more of in 2024.
